<br>
The problem with any 'hidden mechanics' question that Mythic anwsers is that they have been proven wrong by solid (read: lots and lots and lots of logs) player testing in the past. And with the 'DW over 50' question being so hard to test, there's no way to be 100% sure if Mythic is right, or they just think they are. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#c0c0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=barlypoptart>Barlypop Tart</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Journeyman</span><br>  Posts: 14<br> <font color=#000000>(7/25/03 5:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=293.topic&index=15>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.accucom.net/darien/barly/postal.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Wondering if ....</span><hr size=1> AoM is good to have.. AoM 2 with determination 4 = hardly rooted,stuned,mezed merc and tons of resists..<br>
